text: Ana Celia de Armas Caso (born 30 April 1988) is a Cuban-Spanish actress. In 2015, she starred in her first American movie, Knock Knock, followed by Exposed, Hands of Stone, and War Dogs. In 2017, she had her breakout role as AI hologram Joi in the critically acclaimed science fiction movie Blade Runner 2049. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban actors
